Executive Profile
Scott C. Arves  Consultant and Non-Independent Director, TFI International Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships61C$80,350
Background

		Mr. Scott C. Arves has been the Advisor at Transport Corporation of America, Inc. since June 01, 2015. Mr. Arves serves as Consultant of TransForce Inc. He served as the Chief Executive Officer and President at Transport Corporation of America, Inc. and Transport America, Inc. from 2006 to 2015. Prior to joining Transport America, he had a 27-year career with Schneider National, Inc., where he served as the President of the Transportation Sector from May 2000 to June ... 2006. He served as the President of Schneider and was responsible for all of Schneider's trucking and intermodal business, which was a 3 billion business employing approximately 20,000 people. He has been an Independent Director of Commercial Vehicle Group, Inc. since July 29, 2005 and Transport America, Inc. since January 2007. He has been a Non-Independent Director of TFI International Inc. since April 20, 2016. He served as a Director of Transport Corporation of America, Inc. Mr. Arves holds a Bachelor's degree in Industrial Engineering from the University of Wisconsin—Madison.Read Full Background




