Scott C. Arves

Age : 60Public asset : 909,271 USDLinked companies :  TFI International Inc -  Commercial Vehicle Group, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. Scott C. Arves is on the Board of Directors at TFI International, Inc. and Commercial Vehicle Group, Inc. Mr. Arves was previously employed as President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Transport Corp of America, Inc., President-Transportation by Schneider National, Inc., and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Transport America, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Wisconsin.



